    <section class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold border-b-2 border-gray-300 pb-2 mb-4">Experience</h2>
      <div class="space-y-6">
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold">Freelance Software Engineer</h3>
          <p class="text-md text-gray-600">Self-Employed | 2023 - Present</p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside mt-2 space-y-1">
            <li>Developed and deployed full-stack web applications for various clients, focusing on performance and user experience.</li>
